#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:6
msgid "9.0.2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:8
msgid ""
"VTK 9.0.2 collects fixes to 9.0.1 which have been made since its release. Of "
"particular interest are the fixes to macOS rendering, support for the macOS "
"arm64 platform, and updates for API changes in external libraries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:12
msgid "New classes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:14
msgid ""
"Added a `vtkImageProbeFilter` which works like `vtkProbeFilter`, but for "
"`vtkImageData`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:17
msgid "New support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:19
msgid ""
"`enum class` setters and getters are now supported via `vtk{Get,Set}"
"EnumMacro`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:22
msgid "Fixes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:24
msgid "The `QVTKRenderWidget.h` is now installed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:25
msgid "`vtk3DLinearGridPlaneCutter` guards against `nullptr` points and cells"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:26
msgid "The composite date mapper now iterates over data blocks properly"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:27
msgid "`vtkStringArray::Resize` takes tuple elements into account"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:28
msgid ""
"`vtkArrowSource` now supports scalong and rotation around the origin or the "
"arrow's center point"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:30
msgid ""
"The `VTK::DomainsChemistryOpenGL2`, `VTK::RenderingContextOpenGL2`, and "
"`VTK::RenderingOpenGL2` modules are added to the `Rendering` group to avoid "
"missing implementations of rendering components"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:33
msgid ""
"`vtkCutter` enables point merging when requested through a `vtkPointLocator` "
"which merges points"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:35
msgid ""
"`vtkAxesActor` bounds calculations improved to avoid assumptions about range "
"values"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:37
msgid ""
"`vtkWindowLevelLookupTable` out-of-range colors are now initialized properly"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:39
msgid ""
"`vtkImageReslice::RequestInformation` is refactored handle common image "
"information passing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:41
msgid ""
"`vtkImageReslice` creates a new interpolator in `::GetInterpolator`; this "
"new interpolator now uses the same interpolation mode as `vtkImageReslice` "
"itself"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:45
msgid "macOS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:47
msgid "macOS wheels are now built and uploaded by VTK's CI"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:48
msgid "Fixes for macOS OpenGL state tracking (related to `GL_SCISSOR`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:49
msgid ""
"Multisampling on macOS with Intel graphics turned off for volume rendering"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:50
msgid ""
"OpenGL state tracking on macOS with layers is improved (rather than using "
"the wrong context between layers)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:52
msgid "OSPRay is disabled when running under macOS Rosetta"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:54
msgid "Third Party"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:56
msgid "HDF5 has been updated to address errors on newer Xcode compilers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:57
msgid "HDF5 macOS universal2 compilation fixes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:58
msgid "`VTK::mpi` now disables C++ bindings for SGI MPT as well"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:59
msgid "Usage of `numpy.character` is removed (deprecated in NumPy 1.19)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:60
msgid "Avoidance of APIs deprecated in Python 3.9"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:61
msgid ""
"Compilation with newer libfreetype resolved (`FT_CALLBACK_DEF` usage removed)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:64
msgid "9.0.3"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:66
msgid ""
"A minor patchset on top of 9.0.2 to fix problems with the new release "
"process' configuration when building the wheels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:69
msgid "Wheels"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:71
msgid "Disable `VTK_DEBUG_LEAKS` in wheel builds"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.0-stripped.md:72
msgid "Remove long-deprecated API usage in the Python bindings"
msgstr ""
